{"tid":1838970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1月24日 星期五 2000-2200 荔枝角:銀髮族三十晚聲援被囚人士","createTime":"2020-01-24T08:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:00:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5a965c1377c3c03c626692051a826e8f8f1796","tid":1838970,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"1月24日 星期五 2000-2200 荔枝角:銀髮族三十晚聲援被囚人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">荔枝角:銀髮族三十晚聲援被囚人士</span><br />\n日期 : 1月24日 星期五<br />\n時間 : 2000-2200<br />\n地點 : 荔枝角收押所正門大閘外<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對知書</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/82759226_1000578406987650_9171989994472996864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlBJvt_-DS3izkgYXmekUHx0zZfJ2u8ts-BrGksHzpgAIeRXys59V5z4XkOkCNadDg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=ae768ed67e8652f764de9470f11062c8&amp;oe=5E9DED02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F82759226_1000578406987650_9171989994472996864_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlBJvt_-DS3izkgYXmekUHx0zZfJ2u8ts-BrGksHzpgAIeRXys59V5z4XkOkCNadDg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dae768ed67e8652f764de9470f11062c8%26oe%3D5E9DED02&h=08bb3741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【銀髪族年三十晚聲援被囚人士】<br />\n*已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n年三十晚集會要人！希望大家能夠抽時間出席！亦希望我哋嘅聲音同埋歌聲能夠傳到去各位被囚手足的耳中。<br />\n<br />\n🎤出席者（排名不分先後):<br />\n程翔<br />\n伍月蘭 深水埗區區議員<br />\n劉偉聰 Lawrence Lau 深水埗區區議員<br />\n馬屎埔陳伯<br />\n黃衍仁<br />\nStefano Lodola 意大利歌唱家<br />\nPepper Band<br />\n銀髮族一眾發起人<br />\n<br />\n📣銀髮族集會守則，希望能保平安！<br />\n1. 確診武漢肺炎已傳到香港，前來集會必定要戴口罩。<br />\n2. 自備水樽，乾糧，藥油，保暖衣物。<br />\n3. 自行製作文宣品。<br />\n4. 全程Be water。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年1月24日（五）<br />\n時間：晚上八時至十時<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所正門外<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情🔎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/995774120801412/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F995774120801412%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=dc6575d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/995774120801412/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#撐手足撐到底<br />\n#和勇不分齊上齊落<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\nRef : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1000578403654317/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilverhairgroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.845823422463150%2F1000578403654317%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=d2f6ae3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1000578403654317/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"9c053ca5819cc0990b6f269b63274cb231561774","tid":1838970,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5935cdd8b3b7be2af9687803b208caed2f779421","tid":1838970,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752399d6261f314e6ec7f996b01d9e746f79a1fc","tid":1838970,"uid":308588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:2